<p>Some form elements vary their style and rendering between operating systems and browsers. This is why Basecoat provides an ultra lightweight jQuery plugin to skin checkboxes, radio buttons and selects with a normalized skin which you can extend, while retaining accessibility via keyboard, mouse or touch events. To see more information about these plugins check out the sections for <a href="components.html#checkboxjs">Checkboxjs</a> and <a href="components.html#selectjs">Selectjs</a> in the <a href="components.html">Components page</a>. All selects are skinned by default, no class is needed.</p>

